nodes.text: Benicio Del Toro (born February 19, 1967) is an Academy Award–winning Puerto Rican actor known for his roles in such films as Licence to Kill, The Usual Suspects, Traffic, Sin City, Che, and Guardians of the Galaxy. He portrayed DJ in Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi.
